title: 48 in. Wood Handle Ditching Shovel
description: The Razor-Back ditching shovel is designed for digging and clearing drainage, ditches and trenches. The 5 in. open-back industrial gauge tempered steel blade has a rolled step to prevent material build-up. 48 in. premium northern hardwood handle for strength to withstand digging and clearing drainage. Excellent tool for homeowners and professionals.
